Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:36.40,Maihou,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,31st - Gala Concert
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought if I came to the music room,\Nyou'd be here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have no way of contacting you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know your phone number\Nor your email address.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...don't know anything about you, do I?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:00:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kao-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She collapsed, and she's in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuhara University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.65,0:01:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there! How'd it go yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to contact you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I wasn't quite up to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and so I thought if you could withdraw...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Some cake from Yoshitomo.\NGirls like that stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her family runs a cake shop, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's the thought that counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We brought you something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well? How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never better! I'm just in here for tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you miss not seeing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure I missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Twice in such a short time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you were in here for tests\Nthe other day, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That time, it was for new tests,\Njust for the heck of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it's also so I can rest up,\Nand take more time to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You just leered at me\Nwith a dirty look in your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lusting after me\Nno matter where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An invalid! Is it because\NI'm an invalid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't! I didn't lust after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, that was a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't show up, and next thing\Nwe hear, you're in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was a shock for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I stumbled\Nand hit my head, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blood came gushing out! In spurts,\Nyou know! In spurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was so stunned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My parents totally lost it\Nand sent me right to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now we're all caught up.\NOh, the fig tart for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've always tired easily, but lately\NI've had to expend a lot of energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess I pushed myself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's expending energy as she eats.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you some books, too!\NYou've got nothing to do in here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are these books from the library?\NDid you bring them without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are some about music, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's she gonna do\Nwith a ton of books?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kao-chan, you'll be coming back\Nto school by the second semester, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must be imagining things.\NThat answer just now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To think that it seemed rehearsed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Kaori-chan. Let's hook up\Nin our dreams, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to read all these...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.30,MSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei Arima
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have your friends gone home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then can we...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please resume the IV drip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:36.32,MSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Ah"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai just texted me.\NHe says, "Let's go to the festival today."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai? You mean Saito-senpai?\NYou haven't broken up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? It's not like\NI don't like him anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then do you like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:06:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've always had a crush on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about Arima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck are you\Nbringing up Kousei now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-Th-That's so ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we were little,\Nwe've always done everything together,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and rather than someone\Nof the opposite sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see him as a kid brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kid brother again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to jinx yourself by chanting\Nthat "kid brother, kid brother" curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're too scared not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because the comfortable relationship you\Nhave right now would be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was saving that omelette for last!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chose the wrong method of attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arima-kun was afraid,\Nbut he still took the plunge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, there'll be no\Nturning back, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, a yukata!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good on you!\NYou look really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you don't have to be nice.\NClothes make the man, as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did I tell you, Kashiwagi?\NKousei would never say that to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because he only sees me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a nagging big sister or something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day of the festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stand there. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, on second thought, I'll stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are fidgety. Suspicious, much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're gonna be okay, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not lying about being tested, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not gonna tell me you're\N never coming back to school, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're gonna start cussing\Nme out again, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can talk in the music room again, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari-kun was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what he brought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watari.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea. I hear you played alone\Nat the gala concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari-kun told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The accompanist playing a solo?\N That's unheard of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a show-off are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was a gala concert for violinists,\Nso it doesn't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh! Are you an idiot?\NMy sides are splitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? Anyone would've\Nexpected you to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At first... It was because\Nsomeone insulted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But then midway through,\Nthe sound disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's words, her gestures, her smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:09:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My memories of my mother turned\Ninto notes, and flew away into the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're an artist no matter what,\Naren't you? Kousei Arima...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah... Just as I thought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That song... She chose that song for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Love's Sorrow. This song\Nreminds me of my mother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The scent of fabric softener. The sound\Nof the piano as I looked up drowsily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A quiet lullaby.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The smell of antiseptic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Footsteps ringing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A linoleum floor, cloudy and white.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All overlapping with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could've heard it, your piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're okay, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could've played with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're gonna be fine, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not lying about the tests, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:10:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not gonna tell me you're\N never coming back to school, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can see you again, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That you called me by my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You won't leave me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...like my mother did, will you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Sumiya Baseball Youth Sports Club\Nspecial boot camp for sluggers will now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna play video games!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Ten sets of ten sprints\Ndown the beach! Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't play baseball. So how come?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even people who play the piano\Nneed to build up their legs! I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You said "I think!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tiny footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They are not! It's just that\Nyour feet are huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that any way to talk to a maiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei, let's go to Ouji Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could, but I've got piano lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna show him a mud ball\Nas shiny as a rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, if I say so myself.\NIt's a masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I'll make one for Kousei, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei, let's play catch.\NI just learned how to throw a sinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei-kun's going to be a pianist, so he's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would he do if he hurt his hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scrub, scrub.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scrub, scrub.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scrub, scrub, scrub, scrub.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear Arima-kun's skipping school
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to practice the piano, because\Nhe's got a competition coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}O Vreneli, where is your home?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My home is in Switzerland{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is by the beautiful lake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yo ho ho, tra la la la{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hate music!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you practicing hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're slacking off because\NI'm not watching you, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me to practice!\NEvery single day, both Hanon and Czerny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not nearly enough!\NPractice Chopin, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When am I supposed to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Practice Liszt, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what this\Nis about, but calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about stuff\Nwe don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Back off, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm turning to you\Nbecause I can't back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in girls\Nwho aren't in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All the more refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If someone tells her, "You're wrong,"\Nyou know she's gonna sulk,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and get all stubborn, and then\Nthings will get complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when it comes to Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Agreed. I don't relish the thought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I... I want Tsubaki to smile again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she gets all bruised and battered,\NTsubaki's still gonna have to realize it herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that the guy by her side\Nisn't her kid brother at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari-senpai, the scrimmage\Nis about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that kind of thing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...usually, you don't realize it\Ntill it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Arima!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you made up your mind yet?\NYou're the only holdout in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What school you want to\Ngo to. High school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:14:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what made me think...\NThat I'd like to become a really weird pianist!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should give it some thought.\NBut let me know soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}High school,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the future...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who do I want to become?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He dropped it on the beach, and wouldn't\Nstop crying, so I gave him my popsicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then he says he wished\Nit was milk-flavored!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Hey, sorry. There I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's fun\Nto hear about Arima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There I go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you live next door to each other,\Nso of course you have the same memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's like your kid brother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's not! I'm not Kousei's babysitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then... what am I?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're next-door neighbors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the boy who's smaller than me,\Nwho lost his mother at a young age,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who I can't help doting on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the one I wished\Nwould get back on his feet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you, an idiot?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use your heart to solve\Nthose kinds of problems.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! I can't make sense\Nof what you're saying these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other day, you told me that\Nyou "didn't dislike" Saito-senpai, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Like" and "don't dislike" are millions of\Nlight-years apart, you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like? Don't dislike? I don't know\Nwhat you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You need to be honest with yourself\Nand admit it, or someone's going to get hurt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you dislike me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the senpai\NI always had a crush on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then do you like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is it that I like?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like. Don't dislike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dislike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dislike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dislike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dislike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dislike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Are you hurt?\NSick? Is it food poisoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't scavenge for food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got a call from Kashiwagi-san.\NShe said you were in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy, she got me. Who knew\NKashiwagi-san would pull a prank like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So she's human, too, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is strangely compelling,\Ncoming from Kashiwagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was running around like crazy\Nbecause I believed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dripping with sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want a popsicle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milk-flavored again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's what I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The moon's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm hearing it ad nauseam\Nfrom the house next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't play it that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Talking like we always do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could hear some really lousy playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The banter... joking around...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're bigger than mine.\NThese are a boy's footsteps.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei, you've changed somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So weird...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If our eyes happen to meet,\Nmy heart flip-flops.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You did change. With you, I can tell right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's because summer is coming to an end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes sparkle now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They light up, like the headlights of a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you're playing the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was pouring out of you... this gentleness,\Nand a desire to convey something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you're shouting to the world,\N"I'm right here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the kind of pianist\Nwho can convey all that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're an artist no matter what, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go to a high school\Nwith a music course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Music course?\NAre there any around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll be leaving home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroko-san said I only had to go\Nto class twice a week or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'm not sure that I'll get in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I sat out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Again. Here it is again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Music is taking Kousei\Nfar away from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dummy! Kousei, you dummy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go wherever you want, dummy Kousei!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're next-door neighbors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the boy who's smaller than me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who lost his mother at a young age,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who I can't help doting on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the one I wish\Nwould get back on his feet.{\i0}
